==English==
===Adjective===
'''immortal'''

# Not susceptible to death

====Antonyms====
*[[mortal]]

====Etymology====
From Latin adjective '''[[immortalis]]''', from prefix '''[[im-]]''', ''not'', from '''[[in-]]''', + adjective '''[[mortalis]]''', ''mortal'', from '''[[mors]]''' (combining form '''[[mort-]]'''), ''death'', + adjective suffix '''[[-alis]]'''.

